lead_paragraph: West Ham United marked their first match at the Olympic Stadium with a 3-0 win over Slovenian side NK Domzale on Thursday, Cheikhou Kouyate scoring twice to help secure a place in the Europa League playoff round.

headline.print_headline: West Ham Start Life at New Home With Emphatic Win
